msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/WebhooksAdminPage.php:227
msgid "auto-generated if blank"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/WebhooksAdminPage.php:229
msgid "Used to sign every payload via HMAC-SHA256. The receiver computes the same HMAC over the raw request body and compares against the X-WB-Gam-Signature header. If you leave this blank, a 32-byte random secret is generated for you."
